name: tired pixels #17
description:
What do you do with gifts in real life?
It happens that they are not useful to you and gather dust in the closet?
I love the wool socks I got as a gift. I don't need paints and brushes. I and so like a puddle of gasoline in appearance.
a gift that doesn't take up space....
there is something in it.
if only he was beautiful and useful
